title: Giants, Jets make big jumps in NJ.com NFL Power Rankings
text:
WOODBRIDGE â€” After a big pair of victories in Week 4, both the Giants and Jets made notable jumps in this week's edition of NJ.com's NFL power rankings.
And the Eagles ? They fell down the board after blowing the game down the stretch in a loss to the Redskins .
The concept is pretty simple: Every team in the league is ranked, No. 1 all the way to No. 32. Head-to-head results are important, but not everything. We also take into account injuries, how a team is playing and more.
